&lt;p>We know without desire living is not possible. &lt;br>
It amazes me the way &lt;br>
the concept of desirelessness &lt;br>
has been taught and understood in our society.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>We know a desire and dreams &lt;br>
helps human moving in his life &lt;br>
With desire human eat, drink and walk, &lt;br>
With desire human talk, dance and sing, &lt;br>
With desire human search, paint, and construct. &lt;br>
With the desire, we want to live and die!&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>